o install everything.\n\nTechnologies used include ASP.NET Core3.1, C#, Entity Framework core, JavaScript/jQuery, SQL Server 2017,.\n\nSneakerPremier-RETL\n\nSneakerPremier isRetail POS industry. They have 4 locations at the moment and starting franchises soon. They want to be able to sync sales and customer information. This will be a web and table application which should run on Clover hardware.\n\nTechnologies used include ASP.NET Core3.1, C#, Entity Framework core, JavaScript/jQuery, SQL Server 2017,.\n\nMethodMerchant-RETL\n\nMethod Merchant (godatafeed.com) is a returning client in retail industry. GoDataFeed is a cloud-based suite of multichannel marketing technology removes roadblocks to valid product feeds, enhances product data and streamlines products on Google, Amazon, Walmart and eBay. It's a product data feed platform, streamlines how retailers manage, optimize and publish products across the Web. The platform is fully integrated with over 200 channels, the platform allows retailers to spend less time formatting and enhancing product data so they can spend more time selling.\n\nTechnologies used include ASP.NET Console, C#, JavaScript/jQuery, SQL Server 2017,.\n\nSangomaTechnologies-\n\nTLMC\n\nSangoma, is a leading voice and Unified Communications (UC) solution provider, is doing just that with their award-winning cloud and on-premise UC PBX solutions and continuing product innovation. Sangoma is also the primary developer and sponsor of the Asterisk project, the world's most widely used open source communications software, and FreePBX, the world's most widely used open source PBX software.\n\nTechnologies used include ASP.NET Core3.1, ASP.NET Core API 3.1, C#, Entity Framework core, JavaScript/jQuery, SQL Server 2017, SAGE ERP.\n\n===== PAGE 4 =====\n\n\nEDUCATION\nUPTU\n2010 - 2014\nB.Tech from ITS Engineer College\nScored 64% aggregate in B.Tech degree.\nU.P BOARD\nXII\\(^{th}\\)-Completed in 2010, with aggregate 63% from U.P Board.\n\\( X^\\text{t