s Reservation for creating Tip of\npatient. Other one is Standing Order which is responsible for create re-occurrence\nof Reservation for particular days comes under given time frame.\nThis application has four modules which are as follows: Super Admin, Supervisor,\nUser and Patient.\nSuper Admin is default user of application have authority to create Roles and\nPermissions.\nSupervisor is high authority person who can override the other user.\nThere are multiple user according to work profile, created by Admin like Broker,\nVendor etc... Patient are the insured person and will avail the transport facility\nfor their provide appointment/Pharmacies/Return to home etc...\nTechnologies used include ASP.NET MVC, C#, Entity Framework,\nJavaScript/jQuery, Windows Services, SQL Server 2017, Kendo UI, Azure DevOps.\nDefyMedical-HLTS\nDefyMedical is a Web application comes under health care domain. This will help\nto provide the Blood test to the insured patient comes under the Client having\ntyped with DefyMedical. Core of the application is lab test for patient.\n\n===== PAGE 3 =====\n\n\n\n===== PAGE 4 =====\n\n\nEDUCATION\nUPTU\nB.Tech from ITS Engineer College\n2010 - 2014\nScored 64% aggregate in B.Tech degree.\nU.P BOARD\nXII\\(^{th}\\)-Completed in 2010, with aggregate 63% from U.P Board.\nX\\(^{th}\\)-Completed in 2008, with aggregate 53.00% from U.P Board.\nHOBBIES AND INTERESTS\n- Cricket\n- Reading\n- Music"}
